review: Meenakshi madam behaviour is very good & she remains friendly even it was first appointment with her after 6 months of pregnancy at delhi.No worries in mind while talking to her & she listens & responds calmly...She guides very well in terms of preganancy care & diet plan.Replies to every query in my mind happily....moreover gives her max valuable time to patient which is extremely appreciable......Very much satisfiesd & happy to meet my new Doctor at Delhi.....
She is very sweet and have enough patience to listen your problems. She is very calmly respond to queries.
